Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 22
Set Padding 15
Set Margin 10
Set MarginFill "#674EFF"
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Width 1420
Set Height 1650

Env COLORTERM "truecolor"
Env PS1 ""

Hide
Type "tput civis && clear && /tmp/clone-demo -h && sleep 1"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show
Sleep 1s
Screenshot demo/help.png
